Package instructionpattrns

package instructionpattrns
Contains classes for instruction patterns as implemented by EHExtractor, providing functionality for matching instruction patterns with actual instructions.

The package name 'instructionpattrns' is not a typo. After introduction of the terminology 'instruction patterns' for this functionality in EHExtractor it was discovered that Ghidra has something called 'instruction patterns' as well. Renaming the EHExtractor package to 'instructionpatterns' caused all sorts of strange errors, so it was decided to go with the current name.
